Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Congressman Carlos Gimenez is a tireless Advocate for the people of Florida’s 28th Congressional District. As a career firefighter, Carlos has spent his life putting out the flames of dangerous fires and the flames of the dangerous Biden-Harris Administration. Carlos works to Secure our Border, Strengthen our Military, Support our Law Enforcement and First Responders, Protect our always under siege Second Amendment, and Advance our America First Agenda. Carlos Gimenez has my Complete and Total Endorsement - HE WILL NEVER LET YOU DOWN!
